{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kai-esports-exhibition-komitmen-pt-kai-rangkul-milenial/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"KAI Esports Exhibition: Komitmen PT KAI Rangkul Milenial","content":"\n<p>Kata &#8220;kereta api&#8221; dan &#8220;esports&#8221; memang tidak ada hubungannya sama sekali. Namun di acara KAI Esports Exhibition, keduanya menjadi satu kesatuan yang cukup menarik. KAI Esports Exhibition merupakan event esports yang diadakan di Central Hall B, Jogja Expo Center pada tanggal 10-11 Agustus lalu. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55170\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kai-esports-exhibition-komitmen-pt-kai-rangkul-milenial/attachment/02-kai-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-kai-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports.jpg\" alt=\"Pertandingan ekshibisi Auto Chess. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55170\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-kai-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Pertandingan ekshibisi Auto Chess. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Event ini bertujuan untuk mendukung atlet eSports, terutama kaum milenial yang kreatif dan berkomitmen tinggi untuk mendedikasikan diri mereka menjadi atlet eSports profesional,&#8221; ujar Asdo Artiviyanto selaku Corporate Deputy Director of Passenger Transport Marketing and Sales PT Kereta Api Indonesia. Sebelumnya, PT KAI juga meluncurkan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Loko Esports (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://nextren.grid.id/read/011271499/ini-tim-e-sports-tangguh-dari-pt-kereta-api-indonesia-bernama-loko-e-sports?page=all\" target=\"_blank\">Loko Esport</a>, tim esports yang beranggotakan pegawai PT KAI.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dua game dipertandingkan di KAI Esports Exhibition, yaitu Free Fire dan Mobile Legends. Pemenang kompetisi Free Fire akan menjadi wakil Yogyakarta untuk kompetisi SEACA 2019. Baik kompetisi Free Fire dan Mobile Legends, sang juara pertama mendapatkan uang senilai Rp 10 juta + Rp 2 juta UniPin Credit, sementara juara kedua mendapatkan uang senilai Rp 5 juta + Rp 1 juta UniPin Credit. Juara ketiga Free Fire memperoleh uang senilai Rp 2 juta + Rp 500 ribu UniPin Credit dan juara ketiga Mobile Legends mendapatkan uang senilai Rp 3 juta + Rp 500 ribu UniPin Credit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-franchise-esports-majukan-kompetisi-atau-kucilkan-tim-kecil/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mengenal Franchise Esports: Majukan Kompetisi Atau Kucilkan Tim Kecil?</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55171\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kai-esports-exhibition-komitmen-pt-kai-rangkul-milenial/attachment/03-kai-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-kai-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports.jpg\" alt=\"Main event KAI Esports Exhibition. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55171\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-kai-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Main event KAI Esports Exhibition. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kompetisi Free Fire berlangsung sengit antara 12 tim. Dengan mengusung sistem poin, tim Louvre Indopride, RRQ Hades, Jogja Militan 31, dan Indoglobal Kids mendominasi permainan. RRQ Hades menjadi pemenang kompetisi Free Fire KAI Esports Exhibition dengan raihan 2200 poin dan dua kali Booyah; diikuti oleh Jogja Militan 31 dengan 1320 poin dan Louvre Indopride dengan 1050 poin. RRQ Hades pun berhak atas satu tiket SEACA 2019 pada tanggal 8-10 November mendatang. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sementara itu di final Mobile Legends KAI Esports Exhibition, Lov A dan Novus Esports bersaing dalam format pertandingan Best of 3. Lov A unggul di game pertama, namun Novus Esports berhasil mengimbangi di game kedua. Pada akhirnya, Lov A menjadi juara dengan memenangkan game ketiga. Novus Esports menjadi juara kedua sementara Wheel Loader menjadi juara ketiga.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55172\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kai-esports-exhibition-komitmen-pt-kai-rangkul-milenial/attachment/04-kai-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-kai-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports.jpg\" alt=\"JKT48 tampilkan hiburan musik. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55172\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/04-kai-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>JKT48 tampilkan hiburan musik. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain dua game tersebut, KAI Esports Exhibition juga dimeriahkan oleh pertandingan ekshibisi PES 2019, Auto Chess, serta Tekken 7. Acara ini juga dimeriahkan hiburan oleh JKT48, serta pameran game developer lokal seperti CIAYO Games! </p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"720\" height=\"405\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sovhekvZDOc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"5d2cf2e3-f350-51ea-ae67-0146920b81b9"}}}